Hello chemistry student! You have been studying your chemistry notes all day and lost track of time. Now, you are locked on the top floor of the laboratory with only one way out. You must find the keys to each subsequent floor and leave the building before the timer runs out. But BEWARE of the Lab Rats. They will ask you to correctly answer chemical nomenclature questions before they allow you to pass by them. Find your way to the door. First, go to the cabinets.
